{"tid":2290093,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Marco Rubio回應記者問題時稱拜登為「候任總統」","createTime":"2020-11-17T18:26:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-17T19:11:04.000Z","uid":135274,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e9b7768b114f1153f8a22388dddb6af5059c8197","tid":2290093,"uid":135274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T18:26:42.000Z","msg":"<strong>被問及如何評論無黨派參議員Angus King於拜登上任後可能出任國家情報總監時，Marco Rubio指這是「候任總統」的決定。</strong><br />\n<br />\nRubio made the reference when he was asked by Capitol Hill pool reporters what he made of reports that his colleague, independent Maine Sen. Angus King, could be considered as a candidate to be the next director of national intelligence under a Biden presidency.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Well, that'll be the president-elect's decision obviously,&quot; Rubio told reporters Monday, adding that he's worked well with King in the past.<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Marco Rubio指初步結果顯示拜登會成為總統，但強調特朗普有訴諸法律的權力，假如情況有變屆時需要處理。</strong><br />\n<br />\nRubio, when asked about his reference to Biden as the president-elect, said it's based on the election's outcome.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Ultimately that's what the results, the preliminary results, seem to indicate. You certainly have to anticipate if that's the highest likelihood at this point,&quot; Rubio said. &quot;But obviously the president has legal claims in court and he'll continue to pursue those, and if that changes, obviously, it'll be something we'll have to deal with.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<strong>除Marco Rubio外，曾形容拜登為「候任總統」的共和黨參議員還有明顯較反對特朗普的Mitt Romney和Ben Sasse，以及接近中間派的Lisa Murkowski和Susan Collins。</strong><br />\n<br />\nRubio joins a club of only four other Republican senators who have acknowledged Biden's win. They are Sens. Mitt Romney of Utah, Lisa Murkowski of Alaska, Susan Collins of Maine and Ben Sasse of Nebraska, who have all also congratulated Biden for clinching the White House.<br />\n<br />\n報導來源：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.npr.org/sections/biden-transition-updates/2020/11/16/935594118/sen-rubio-joins-small-group-of-republican-senators-calling-biden-president-elect\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2Fsections%2Fbiden-transition-updates%2F2020%2F11%2F16%2F935594118%2Fsen-rubio-joins-small-group-of-republican-senators-calling-biden-president-elect&d=KoeRi8LHiva86SpHjnbz1ZuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=620e43e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.npr.org/sections/biden-transition-updates/2020/11/16/935594118/sen-rubio-joins-small-group-of-republican-senators-calling-biden-president-elect</a>"},{"pid":"ab695872fe2b8fc6a49f98666704120f851adeec","tid":2290093,"uid":173271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T18:27:52.000Z","msg":"候選總統<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71638cba0f814a89cfb39ca36c7ef42f53e43edd","tid":2290093,"uid":135274,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T18:31:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bf2b7a99e3136319aa207295122cc9029da60fe","tid":2290093,"uid":84668,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T18:32:18.000Z","msg":"得喇<br />\n侵認輸丫嘛"},{"pid":"7e77d6cda0cbd296e24f6ce0061f41369b8852fc","tid":2290093,"uid":383914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T18:32:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc68ef18d1c870cdd94b05dc2a99f7db2decbd54","tid":2290093,"uid":135274,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T18:35:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2ca2ce7a625489327551157839c620abd4221d3","tid":2290093,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T18:38:05.000